  "prompt": "Which is a suitable solar panel installation provider in Sierra Madre, California CA?",
  "response": "There are several solar panel installation providers that have a good reputation in Sierra Madre, California. Some options to consider include:\n\n1. **Sunrun** - One of the largest residential solar companies in the U.S., known for their lease and purchase options.\n2. **Vivint Solar** - Offers a variety of solar solutions and has a focus on customer satisfaction.\n3. **Sierra Solar** - A local company that may offer personalized service and support.\n4. **Tesla Energy** - Known for their solar roofs and energy storage solutions, with installation services across California.\n5. **SunPower** - Offers high-efficiency panels and has a strong reputation for quality.\n\nBefore deciding, it\u2019s advisable to read customer reviews, compare quotes, check for local incentives, and inquire about warranties and maintenance services.",
